{"tid":2369237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp改私隱條款延至5.15 　鄺俊宇：「暫緩唔係撤回，香港人都知啦」","createTime":"2021-01-17T03:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T05:18:52.000Z","uid":271829,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9ecb0052682a023e52e2e97e1a94a04b2fa220a5","tid":2369237,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:28:27.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n【本報訊】通訊軟件WhatsApp早前要求用戶同意新服務條款和私隱政策，包括將用戶的手提電話等個人資料與其母公司facebook共享，用戶紛紛遷徙至Signal、Telegram等其他通訊軟件。WhatsApp周五終於宣佈暫緩修例，宣佈將接受新服務條款的期限，由2月8日押後至5月15日。不過此舉未獲用戶接納，已過戶的元朗區議員鄺俊宇便明言，「暫緩唔係撤回，香港人都知啦」。<br />\n<br />\n網民仍不滿 斥只重視推廣<br />\n聲明重申，由於有大量錯誤資訊流傳引起用戶對軟件更新的誤解，他們須澄清，軟件一直以端對端加密保障用戶個人對話，亦不會儲存用戶傳送訊息的紀錄，不會將聯絡人資訊分享給facebook。<br />\n然而普遍網民並不接納暫緩修例，WhatsApp在facebook專頁的帖文引發數以萬計留言，大多數都是質疑聲音。有網民直斥WhatsApp只視利用用戶資料作廣告及市場推廣，從未關心客戶私隱問題、亦有網民稱不會再相信WhatsApp，所有親友均已轉用Signal等其他通訊軟件。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n[url<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/HTOZ4LXJJVBFJDAZ2JAFMWZMRY/][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FHTOZ4LXJJVBFJDAZ2JAFMWZMRY%2F%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHF6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=c39ccf7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FHTOZ4LXJJVBFJDAZ2JAFMWZMRY%2F%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&h=6e85d2ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/HTOZ4LXJJVBFJDAZ2JAFMWZMRY/][/url]</a>"},{"pid":"607349c6655ed7ca4c89852a286b9ba6e581cd11","tid":2369237,"uid":58841,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp真係當人白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾多三個月signal搞好server<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4336551d10b1bd27c10f3cae8d69c7e37632cea","tid":2369237,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" cl